chore(beans): enforce branch + bean usage in Copilot templates

This draft PR updates the Copilot instruction and skill templates to require agents to:

- create or switch to the bean's branch before editing code or files
- keep all progress and subtasks inside the bean's `## Todo` checklist (no internal agent todo lists)
- always use the MCP or extension for bean creation/edits and not write bean files directly
- only set `branch` and `pr` frontmatter keys from agent automation

Files changed:
- src/beans/config/templates/copilot-instructions.template.md
- src/beans/config/templates/copilot-skill.template.md

Bean: beans-vscode-kcff

This is a draft PR for review.